  <brief_title>Multimodal Analgesia for Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Comparison of Multimodal Analgesic Protocols for Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy: Pharmacologic Interventions and Combination of Pharmacologic and Operative Interventions</official_title>
