  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is important to decrease the postoperative pain in patients undergoing laparoscopic&#xD;
      cholecystectomy. We will compare the pharmacologic analgesia with the parmacologic and&#xD;
      surgical analgesia in patients undergoing laparoscopic cholecystectomy.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
